<li><a href=3D"https://www.cuemath.com/algebra/common-difference/">Common d=
ifference</a>, d</li>
<li>Identify which term you want. i.e., n</li>
<li>Substitute all these into the formula a<sub>n</sub> =3D a + (n =E2=80=
=93 1) =C3=97 d.</li>
</ul></div></div></div><div itemscope=3D"" class=3D"collapsed-question" ite=
mprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/Question"><h3 itemprop=
