div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"suggestedAnswer acceptedAnswer" class=3D"col=
lapsed-answer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text=
"><p>To find the sum of the first n terms of arithmetic sequences,</p><ul>
